label: project
description: “A single Research Project, extended from https://schema.org/Project”

label: project
description: “The research project associated with this dataset”

label: service
description: “the id of a virtual machine or storage service associated with this project"

label: dropbox
description: “the ID of a storage DropBox linked to this project”

label: designation
description: “The sensitivity designation of the data in this project”

label: requirements
description: “Free-text requirements for this projects, e.g. requires human ethics approval”

label: projectOwner
description: “The Owner and primary contact for this project (usually PI)”

label: dataOwner
description: “the Owner of the data in this project”

label: dataContact
description: “A contact for data contained in this project"

label: researchDrive
description: “the research drive of origin for this data”

label: dataClassification
description: “The classification of the data for research data retention and information security.  MUST be ONE of ["Public", "Internal", "Sensitive", or "Restricted"]. Default "Sensitive".

label: division
description: “the division of the school that owns this project”
